The paper is about distributed machine learning with edge systems, which is a topic that falls under the machine learning (cs.LG) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC) categories. The paper also addresses the challenges of heterogeneity in computing capacity, which is a systems and control (cs.SY) issue. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of IoT devices, which falls under the networking and internet architecture (cs.NI) category. Finally, the paper proposes a new parameter synchronization scheme, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
